sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor HR
    actor User as Mahasiswa
    participant App as Mobile/Web App
    participant Backend
    participant Reverb as Laravel Reverb (WebSocket)
    participant DB as Database (PostgreSQL)

    HR->>Backend: Set Geofencing Radius for Location
    Backend->>DB: Save Geofence Data
    
    User->>App: Click Check-in
    App->>Backend: Request Check-in with Current Location
    Backend->>DB: Validate Distance (Haversine Formula)
    alt Within Radius
        Backend->>DB: Save Check-in Status
        Backend-->>App: Check-in Success
        loop Realtime Tracking
            App->>Reverb: Send GPS Coordinates (Realtime)
            Reverb->>Backend: Broadcast Coordinates
            Backend->>DB: Save Temporary Path
        end
    else Outside Radius
        Backend-->>App: Check-in Failed (Out of Zone)
    end

    User->>App: Click Check-out
    App->>Backend: Request Check-out
    Backend->>DB: End Tracking Session
    Backend->>DB: Anonymize/Round off old location history
    Backend-->>App: Check-out Success
